Title: Avalanche An Agent Based Value Chain Coordination Experiment  
Author: Torsten Eymann freiburg.de Boris Padovan freiburg.de Detlef Schoder 
Keyword: Economic Design, Multi-Agent System, Complex Adaptive Systems, Coordination Mechanisms  
